{"data":[{"date":"07:48 31/07","title":"\"Silva \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/silva-dang-trong-giai-doan-tot-nhat-cua-su-nghiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1i t\u00ean David \u2013 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tuy\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla h\u1ebft l\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Silva<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft trong 5 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Valencia, 2 ch\u00e0ng David g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2008 v\u00e0 World Cup 2010. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, c\u1ea3 2 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m chung n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Pep Guardiola t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c nhau (Barca v\u00e0 Man City).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do David Villa hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi Pep c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man City v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. David Silva v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Pep\" title=\"David Silva nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb HLV Pep Guardiola.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/silva-dang-trong-giai-doan-tot-nhat-cua-su-nghiep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Pep</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n sang Barca. Khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Champions League c\u00f9ng Valencia, nh\u01b0ng Pep \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft David Silva khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1ea1i Valencia. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 s\u1ebd hay h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd thay \u0111\u1ed5i tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Man City. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a David, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu con trai c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. David n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 th\u00eam v\u00e0i n\u0103m n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Villa ca ng\u1ee3i Silva.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-192262.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/david-silva-can-nhac-chia-tay-dt-tay-ban-nha-180-192262.html\">David Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf</span><br>\r\nDavid Silva c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 xem x\u00e9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018-329-192238.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-bayern-munich-23-man-city-icc-2018-329-192238.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Bayern Munich 2-3 Man City (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u00f2n v\u00f4 danh \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd. C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1ed9c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1827","checkdouble":"192364"},{"date":"07:17 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sheriff vs Shkendija 00h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-sheriff-vs-shkendija-00h00-ngay-18-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sheriff vs Shkendija l\u00fac 00h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sheriff vs Shkendija 00h00 ng\u00e0y 18 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sheriff vs Shkendija 00h00 ng\u00e0y 18 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Sheriff-vs-Shkendija.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sheriff vs Shkendija</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Sheriff vs Shkendija: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Sheriff \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Macedonia (0-1). Th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Goran Sabli\u0107 v\u1ed1n y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng v\u00eda khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a FC Torpedo Kutaisi, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Georgia (1-2). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i Sheriff s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 1-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a FC Torpedo Kutaisi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i s\u00e0o huy\u1ec7t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Sheriff th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. T\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sabli\u0107 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui \u1edf 8/9 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p TLCA<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Sheriff \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Shkendija. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu Sheriff ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1826","checkdouble":"192365"},{"date":"07:32 31/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Hapoel Beer Sheva vs Dinamo Zagreb 00h00 ng\u00e0y 1/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/nhan-dinh-hapoel-beer-sheva-vs-dinamo-zagreb-00h00-ngay-18-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u2013 Charlie Adam, anh tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAdam t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 Charlie Adam cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Klopp bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n trong khung g\u1ed7. Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 6-8 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Charlie Adam tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League\" title=\"charlie adam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2012/7/Charlie-Adam-Hairstyles-500x375-201271674631.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Charlie Adam tin r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Shaqiri, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu Mohamed Salah c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thay th\u1ebf cho Salah, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Shaqiri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Shaqiri s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Liverpool, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Charlie Adam chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Kop, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\">Van Dijk: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho&hellip; Martial</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u1eafng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1825","checkdouble":"192366"},{"date":"08:43 31/07","title":"Petr Cech \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 Leno: \"Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi Bundesliga\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/petr-cech-dap-tra-leno-ngoai-hang-anh-khac-han-so-voi-bundesliga.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leno quy\u1ebft\u00a0 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 5 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i chi ra 19.3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Petr-Cech-phat-bieu-ve-Bernd-Leno-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leno mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-19-trieu-bang-len-tieng-canh-bao-petr-cech-172-192297.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bernd Leno kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Petr Cech</span> cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u1eaft HLV. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 run s\u1ee3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa t\u00f4i, Cech v\u00e0 Ospina gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno, ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Petr Cech phat bieu ve Leno\" title=\"Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Leno\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/petr-cech-dap-tra-leno-ngoai-hang-anh-khac-han-so-voi-bundesliga.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Petr Cech ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh\u00a0c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede Premier League, m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Leno \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1824","checkdouble":"192367"},{"date":"09:01 31/07","title":"Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Conte song th\u00e0nh t\u00edch m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 20 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Willian-noi-ve-tuong-lai-truoc-tin-don-duoc-MU-va-Real-quan-tam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m Willian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 khi\u1ebfn Mourinho th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford. C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea mu\u1ed1n M.U chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian-180-192290.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian</span>, Los Blancos th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Courtois v\u00e0 Willian. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef Willian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Willian ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n Willian \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018, anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Chelsea. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/chelsea-dong-y-ban-willian-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWillian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Brazil, Esporte Espetacular, Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i\u00a0r\u1ea5t vui \u1edf Chelsea, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi s\u1ed1ng \u1edf London\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia coi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1823","checkdouble":"192368"},{"date":"08:05 31/07","title":"\"Liverpool l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/liverpool-la-ung-cu-vien-hang-dau-cho-danh-hieu-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u2013 Charlie Adam, anh tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAdam t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 Charlie Adam cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Klopp bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n trong khung g\u1ed7. Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 6-8 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Charlie Adam tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League\" title=\"charlie adam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2012/7/Charlie-Adam-Hairstyles-500x375-201271674631.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Charlie Adam tin r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Shaqiri, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu Mohamed Salah c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thay th\u1ebf cho Salah, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd Shaqiri s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Shaqiri s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Liverpool, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Charlie Adam chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Kop, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\">Van Dijk: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Van Dijk tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/29/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-tham-liverpool-mourinho-do-loi-cho-martial-172-192234.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Liverpool, Mourinho \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho&hellip; Martial</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u1eafng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1822","checkdouble":"192369"},{"date":"08:33 31/07","title":"HLV Real x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 Ronaldo m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafm vai ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong ni\u1ec1m vui c\u1ee7a danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Bale b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Zinedine Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Manchester United. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, HLV Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Julen Lopetegui. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t r\u1eddi Real v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/HLV-Julen-Lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-Gareth-Bale-day-tu-tin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real trong t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i xung quanh ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid nh\u01b0ng ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Real. \u201cL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. CLB \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng Gareth Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale cua Real\" title=\"Bale cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV\u00a0Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Neymar, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos song h\u1ecd v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Real Madrid\u201d, Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man United t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 HLV h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3 thuy\u1ebft. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/hlv-psg-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-edinson-cavani-197-192355.html\">HLV PSG l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n Cavani s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thay-the-ronaldo-gareth-bale-doi-mua-tap-luyen-cung-real-madrid-180-192351.html\">Thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a luy\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chelsea-san-sang-ban-willian-va-courtois-cho-real-voi-mot-dieu-kien-184-192313.html\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-sieu-bao-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-real-172-192304.html\">MU d\u00ednh si\u00eau b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian-180-192290.html\">T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1821","checkdouble":"192371"},{"date":"08:50 31/07","title":"V\u00ec c\u00e2u n\u00f3i n\u00e0y, Pochettino khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Tottenham lo ngay ng\u00e1y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. \u00d4ng th\u00fa nh\u1eadn CLB th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham im \u1eafng tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, Premier League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u01b0 d\u1ea3, nh\u00f3m \u201cBig Six\u201d ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 vung ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Liverpool l\u00e0 h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea v\u00e0 Man City m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 bom t\u1ea5n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mang t\u00ean Jorginho v\u00e0 Ryiad Mahrez. \u0110\u1ebfn Arsenal m\u1ecdi n\u0103m tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng c\u0169ng s\u1edbm mang v\u1ec1 cho m\u00ecnh 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/29/HLV-Pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham kh\u00e1 im \u1eafng tr\u00ean TTCN</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang Tottenham d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a 2017/18, Pochettino th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB n\u00ean \u201cd\u0169ng c\u1ea3m\u201d v\u00e0 \u201cch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn r\u1ee7i ro\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Gareth Bale (Real Madrid), Jack Grealish (Aston Villa) r\u1ed3i Anthony Martial (Man United), Spurs v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino\" title=\"HLV Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o hay kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i cho b\u1ea1n li\u1ec7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 1, 2, 3 hay 4 t\u00e2n binh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Newcastle United v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-gap-kho-vu-mua-grealish-172-192258.html\">Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 mua sao h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192254.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-ra-dieu-kien-mua-alderweireld-cho-mu-172-192150.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao Tottenham, M.U ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\">Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-tai-ngo-modric-172-191894.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Modric</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1820","checkdouble":"192372"},{"date":"08:28 31/07","title":"Video: Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Hulk \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/messi-tap-luyen-voi-hulk-de-chuan-bi-cho-mua-giai-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Hulk \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 xanh, m\u00e0 Leo Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMessi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi ch\u00f3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 s\u1eebng s\u1ecf, m\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Senor Hulk \u2013 ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/messi-tap-luyen-voi-hulk-de-chuan-bi-cho-mua-giai-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Senor Hulk l\u00e0 gi\u1ed1ng ch\u00f3 Dogue de Bordeaux, m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 m\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u00f4m tr\u1ecdn. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, n\u00f3 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n to h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00fa vui \u0111\u1ec3 El Pulga v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng World Cup 2018, khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y ai l\u1ea1i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, khi Senor Hulk to \"t\u1ed5 b\u1ed1\" \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfp v\u00eda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chu cho Senor Hulk ngay nao\" title=\"Ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 Senor Hulk ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/hilk.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00fa ch\u00f3 Senor Hulk ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng xem \u0111o\u1ea1n video Leo Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/31/messi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-chia-se-su-that-thu-vi-ve-messi-180-192363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/yerry-mina-chia-se-su-that-thu-vi-ve-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-chia-se-su-that-thu-vi-ve-messi-180-192363.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U chia s\u1ebb s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 Messi</span><br>\r\nGi\u1eefa tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/vo-chong-messi-lien-tuc-gap-nguoi-noi-tieng-trong-ky-nghi-he-2018-188-192329.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vo-chong-messi-lien-tuc-gap-nguoi-noi-tieng-trong-ky-nghi-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/vo-chong-messi-lien-tuc-gap-nguoi-noi-tieng-trong-ky-nghi-he-2018-188-192329.html\">V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt VIP ch\u1ecdn Ibiza \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t, g\u1eb7p si\u00eau sao Argentina v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1819","checkdouble":"192373"},{"date":"09:03 31/07","title":"VFF treo gi\u00e0y v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/vff-treo-giay-vinh-vien-cau-thu-duoi-danh-trong-tai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn play-off gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>VFF treo gi\u00e0y v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VFF treo gi\u00e0y v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VFF treo gi\u00e0y v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/vff-treo-giay-vinh-vien-cau-thu-duoi-danh-trong-tai.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n v\u00ec \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u2018chung k\u1ebft\u2019 tranh su\u1ea5t th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 18/7 v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1ee5 \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 CLB B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u (BRVT) \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u1ed1 Hi\u1ebfn FC.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a BRVT \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Anh V\u0169 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t khung c\u1ea3nh h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u1ea5t may l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau khi xem x\u00e9t b\u00e1o c\u00e1o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t treo gi\u00f2 v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m \u201c\u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\u201d th\u00e2n th\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. K\u00e8m theo \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p ph\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32 c\u00f9ng sai ph\u1ea1m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Ngo\u00e0i Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a CLB B\u00e0 R\u1ecba V\u0169ng T\u00e0u c\u0169ng \u201cl\u0129nh \u0111\u1ea1n\u201d kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng g\u1ed3m Phan C\u00f4ng Qu\u1ef3nh Anh v\u00e0 \u0110inh Ti\u1ebfn Phong. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 18 th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u00f3ng ph\u1ea1t 17,5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u00f9ng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Hu\u1ef3nh Qu\u1ed1c Long, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m th\u00e2n th\u1ec3 Qu\u1ed1c Tu\u1ea5n. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n \u00e1n n\u00eau tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i l\u00ean Ban gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i VFF. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u00e1n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/19/cau-thu-vung-tau-duoi-danh-trong-tai-1531913303.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1818","checkdouble":"192374"},{"date":"21:56 30/07","title":"Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \"ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joe Gomez, HLV Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o cho Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp tin v\u00e0o Joe Gomez<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 174 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed1n c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker, Naby Keita, Fabinho v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u suy \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng Liverpool s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool t\u1eebng chi ra 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a The Kop c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn, ngo\u00e0i Van Dijk c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Ragnar Klavan, Dejan Lovren, Joel Matip v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Joe Gomez.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joe Gomez: \"C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joe Gomez m\u00e0 HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 cho Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 Fabinho hay James Milner c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Klopp t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Kop.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb: \"C\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n 12 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa trong th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. N\u00ean gi\u1edd t\u00f4i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ebfn mai khi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecfi, c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t khi th\u1eafng Man City v\u00e0 Man Utd trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\">Van Dijk: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aston-villa-hoi-muon-ben-woodburn-172-192317.html\">Aston Villa h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n sao tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-mu-klopp-danh-loi-ca-ngoi-cho-1-cai-ten-172-192240.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t M.U, Klopp d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-14-liverpool-icc-2018-326-192224.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-4 Liverpool (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-dat-nhat-the-gioi-klopp-van-khen-re-172-192219.html\">Alisson \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Klopp v\u1eabn khen... r\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-xet-liverpool-tiet-lo-dang-yeu-lai-tu-dau-voi-klopp-172-192212.html\">Sao x\u1eb9t Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang \u201cy\u00eau l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d v\u1edbi Klopp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"