u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Ronaldo, khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Neymar, Mbappe hay Eden Hazard g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/5/Thomas-Tuchel-phat-bieu-ve-Edinson-Cavani-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cavani, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong l\u1eabn ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987, Real Madrid ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani-180-192189.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cavani</span> cho Los Blancos. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ef1u sao Napoli n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n Cavani r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi, Morata v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dortmund mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Edinson Cavani, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban tu da phat de giai cuu PSG\" title=\"Cavani ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/23/psg-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-vu-edinson-cavani.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tuchel mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Cavani \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Cavani, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, Cavani kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf PSG v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCavani l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a PSG, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. PSG s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Cavani, \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi. PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1815","checkdouble":"192352"},{"date":"00:32 31/07","title":"Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp: Ai chi ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea1o chi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u00edn, m\u1ed9t m\u01b0\u1eddi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu x\u00e9t t\u1eeb c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c th\u00e1ng 5/2016 khi Jose Mourinho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch nhau l\u00e0 bao. Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 411.55* tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn trong n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho va Jurgen Klopp deu chi rat nhieu tien tren thi truong chuyen nhuong.\" title=\"Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Klopp th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Liverpool chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Virgil Van Dijk. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Klopp b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam b\u1ed1n g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker (67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Naby Keita (53.75), Fabinho (43) v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri (13.5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho trong hai n\u0103m qua c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Man Utd s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 392.55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man Utd chi ra tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda Liverpool v\u1edbi ba b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Fred (53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Diogo Dalot (19) v\u00e0 Lee Grant (1.5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh hi\u1ec7u, Jose Mourinho \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Man Utd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Carabao Cup 2016-17, Europa League 2016-17 v\u00e0 FA Community Shield 2016. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jurgen Klopp ba l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 l\u00e3i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Jurgen Klopp l\u1ea1i nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 289.65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong hai n\u0103m qua, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 The Kop ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 chi ra 121.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 85.3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Man Utd ph\u1ea3i b\u00f9 th\u00eam ra l\u1edbn g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i Liverpool v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 307.25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>* S\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Sky Sports.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Mourinho v\u00e0 Klopp:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-co-nguy-co-bi-sa-thai-cao-nhat-tai-premier-league-172-192349.html\">Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd-184-192346.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 30/7: Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u nh\u00f3m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-mourinho-can-lam-de-cuu-van-tour-du-dau-tham-hoa-cua-mu-172-192341.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve-172-192350.html\">Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-mu-klopp-danh-loi-ca-ngoi-cho-1-cai-ten-172-192240.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t M.U, Klopp d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-dat-nhat-the-gioi-klopp-van-khen-re-172-192219.html\">Alisson \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Klopp v\u1eabn khen... r\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1814","checkdouble":"192353"},{"date":"06:17 31/07","title":"Cesar Azpilicueta n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte</span> v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t l\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00edch nghi t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Azpilicueta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 khi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Azpilicueta noi ve tran dau Barca vs Chelsea\" title=\"Azpilicueta n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/Azpilicueta-phat-bieu-ve-tinh-canh-bi-dat-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Cesar Azpilicueta th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o th\u00ec anh c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1813","checkdouble":"192354"}]}